Subject: Bulk Effective Access
Description: There is functionality to gain effective access for Group NTAccounts in the AIC but we have a need to produce these in bulk. Can you please advise if this is possible via MSSQL
What_We_Know__c: The customer wants to be able to search by multiple resources. As they put it. if this page can be shown (i.e. this data exists in the DB) then there should be a way to produce this page 740 times without going to each individual resource. Custom SQL query or a custom report should do the trick.
Next_Steps__c:
I believe we found a way to modify the Ad Hoc trustees job to allow group permissions. 
Haven't had a chance to review with Graham on results.
Solution_Comment__c:
Advised how we can modify current Trustees job for this, but its not really the intention.
Professional services would be better suited.
